Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你已經有能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你最後抵達的地方 將是你容身的原野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們是來鬧的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼討厭眼睛能束縛你們手腳的她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她要是想念這個家 自然會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且要把她帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非人類的樣子會更方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為人的生命 比森林之影中誕生的半成品更為脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們都這麼稱呼我 疏遠我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我討厭寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太叫人憐愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好美麗 好快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是…什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彷彿有人在我耳邊叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺自己哪裡都可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甚至是荒無人煙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 因為有人在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想走的話 我陪你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你對那邊已經沒有留念了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是什麼人來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 我還有很多東西不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世不在 我會很頭痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你會頭痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還會很冷 很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不喜歡寒冷 所以我這就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺還迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是詛咒的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}詛咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是變身人狼所用的毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過現在是狐狸皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人狼的毛皮會回應人的訴求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是份不懷好意的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要用得先問過我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他那種人就叫做愉快犯 還跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是我真的去了那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世不想去的話 我會阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算我想也要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救救喬伊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他一整天都沒起床
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我實在是無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是把好鎖 古老的鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是最適合你的油 我是你的金鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喬伊爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喬伊爺爺 喬伊爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到你突然衝出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個男人怎麼了 他好像快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魅魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他是你的獵物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對 我沒有吃他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有吸一滴血 沒有碰他一點生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被吸血鬼附身 就決定了他的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒有附身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得離開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要我走得遠遠的 喬伊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你已經對這個男人下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論你離多遠都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 你能看一下喬伊爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒有愛他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我根本就沒有愛上他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我們要是相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就要將這份愛情堅持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是死神什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}類似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我家的孩子受您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她名叫智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你應該活不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去醫院也治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}善良的死神先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我這把老骨頭還能活多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最多一個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會很痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就好 我的一生也滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您不覺得害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然害怕 誰都怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是死亡是不可逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的妻子先我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然是父母之命 並非戀愛結的婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我還是很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但妻子留下的玫瑰園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把我從悲傷中拉了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許是正午陽光下的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我又有了次難忘的美好邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但如果有緣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好想再見那個長著紅醋栗眼眸的人一面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見一次面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要做妖精的藥膏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以製作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要把它塗在眼皮上 就能讓普通人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就能讓喬伊爺爺看到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那東西基本上不能對人類使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是被鄰居們知道了 她們會大為憤怒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我只希望他們相見一眼都好 聊一句話都好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然我是想這麼說 但這次可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是你第一次對我任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是不要勉強自己 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是不能維持住那個狀態就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且這次我不能出手幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我也幫不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精討厭被人看到 哪怕是使魔也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 你覺得我一個人做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的身體狀況還不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果可以 我是不希望你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但只有這次 我想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使用魔法的時候 我會雙眼盯緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就能看到身邊四處飄浮 嬉戲著的光點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這應該就是所謂的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}顏色就像夜空中的繁星一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是有時 會變成大海一般的湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也會變成森林一般的翠綠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有時又像朝霞一樣白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:13:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像裝進搖籃裡一般 聚集起它們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 看起來沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後要保持好這個狀態五天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對不能勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼問題要跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彷彿身體裡有種寶貴的東西在溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把古老的金幣放進汲來的泉水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}調入當季才開的花朵做成的香料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在滿月之日放置一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以及東南西北的窗邊各放一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓其充分沐浴日光與月光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這期間 必須待在藥瓶的旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連睡覺也不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算如此 成功的機率也只有五成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你願意為我做到這種地步？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們的行為 其實也是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是希望對我笑過的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能夠因為我 保持住他們的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類真是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且也很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天是第幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第四天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一股味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是祝福的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可是件有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕 我睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊 已經成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然差點失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 你拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}順你的心意去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做夢了嗎 剛剛還起不來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像睡了很久似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於和你 相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是因為你…找到了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我…才沒辦法離開你的身邊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我聽你說害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}害怕一個人離開人世的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你愛上了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魅魔 詩人的戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:14.63,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fs32}※凱爾特神話中，魅魔會給予憑依的人藝術和詩作的才華，被認為是所有凱爾特詩人的戀人。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這點事我心裡也清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你不嫌棄我這年邁的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就請都收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 可是我總是收到你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你什麼都沒有得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:41.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}時の砂場で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:49.43,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}やっと聞こえた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:58.31,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}柔らかな鼓動の音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:07.74,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}触れることさえできない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:15.22,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}愛の陽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:23.37,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}裸足で駆けて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:32.16,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}あなたとは反対側
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:39.04,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}追いかけた春の日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:46.71,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}風の中を砂が舞った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:55.15,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}もしこの世がビンの底なら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:20:03.89,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}逆さにして　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:14.24,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}あなたと明日を描くのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:18.12,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}愛し欠けた月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:22.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}最後にください
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:26.12,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}ほんの一秒を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.37,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}ほんの一秒を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.06,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}剥がれ堕ちた星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.54,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}頬を伝い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:43.93,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}暁を照らした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:41.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}光陰的沙海間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:49.43,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:58.31,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}那柔軟的心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:07.74,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我卻無法觸及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:15.22,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}愛的熱流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:23.37,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}光著腳跑過身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:32.16,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}那是我在你的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:39.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}追逐著你的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:46.71,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}劃過的風中 帶著砂礫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:55.15,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}如果世界 躲在瓶底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:20:03.89,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我願倒過瓶口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:14.24,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}無數次 與你描繪明天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:18.12,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}心愛的半月喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:22.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我還有最後的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:26.12,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}請再給我一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.37,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}請再給我一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.06,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}滑落的顆顆星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}淌過我臉頰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:43.93,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}映出了拂曉的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和妻子生死別離以後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就只是為了活而活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但突然有一天 有一刻見到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好美 我好想能再見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:19:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就此 我的人生有了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽到這話 我不是更加離不開你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道自己會去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許能到達妻子的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我一定 也一定會去往你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要不孤單 有等候我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就一點都不害怕 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的生命 你就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 我還沒回答你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類真是好笨 好任性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}永遠地等下去 等著喬伊再回到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}悲傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是看到你流眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體裡就會有些不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 不能成為你的教師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 還是快回去躺下休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奧布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精的藥膏 「眼皮上的祝福」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類是不可以做這種藥的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 剩下的能交給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請拿去
